    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The coffee here must be strong or the cake is just a walnut sponge with a beige frosting. ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "Coffee extract",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "term": "Coffee extract",
                  "termId": "cmpbjxijb0000u0v4eeppwwmr"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " or a very concentrated shot of espresso is what actually delivers the flavour. The walnuts go in the batter and onto the top; they are load-bearing, not decorative.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
